==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sentence method
<hw>Sen"tence meth`od</hw>. <fld>(Education)</fld> <def>A method of
teaching reading by giving first attention to phrases and sentences and
later analyzing these into their verbal and alphabetic components; --
contrasted with <contr>alphabet method</contr> and <contr>word
method</contr>. See also <contr>phonics</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sentencer</ent>⟦br⟧
